title: Brideshead Revisited.BBC.1981.Subs.Swe.Es.E02.Home.and.Abroad
description:
Swedish and Spanish Subs for Episode 1 included.
Episode 2: "Home and Abroad" (Original UK airdate 20 October 1981; 53 minutes) At Brideshead, Charles is introduced to Sebastian's younger sisters Julia and Cordelia and his older brother Brideshead ('Bridey'). The two young men decide to accept an invitation to Venice extended by Sebastian's father, Lord Marchmain, who lives there with his mistress Cara.
